# Codegen: use `npm run codegen`

Never recreate a package's `generated/` folder by hand or run `graphql-codegen`/`buf` ad hoc. From the repo root:

```bash
npm run codegen
```

This runs every package's `prebuild.sh` (`firebase/functions/prebuild.sh`, `web/core/prebuild.sh`, `web/app/prebuild.sh`) in the right order: protos, GraphQL resolver types, JSON schema definitions for backend-driven forms, and typed client hooks.

Run it after any change to `Graphql/**/*.gql` or `protobufs/**/*.proto`. Never edit files under any `generated/` directory.
